statements: SELECT * FROM backlink_data ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT url, anchor_text, source_domain FROM backlink_data WHERE backlink_status='Active';
SELECT * FROM backlink_data WHERE source_domain LIKE '%example.com%' ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT id, backlink_status, backlink_type FROM backlink_data WHERE backlink_status='Inactive';
SELECT source_domain, COUNT(*) AS total_backlinks FROM backlink_data GROUP BY source_domain ORDER BY total_backlinks DESC;
SELECT * FROM backlink_data WHERE backlink_status = 'active';
SELECT id, url, anchor_text FROM backlink_data WHERE source_domain = 'example.com';
SELECT * FROM backlink_data WHERE backlink_type = 'dofollow' ORDER BY id DESC;
SELECT url, backlink_status FROM backlink_data WHERE anchor_text LIKE '%SEO%' AND backlink_status = 'active';
SELECT id, source_domain, backlink_status FROM backlink_data WHERE source_domain LIKE '%.org%' ORDER BY source_domain ASC, id ASC;
SELECT * FROM backlinks WHERE backlink_status = TRUE;
SELECT backlink_id, anchor_text, source_domain FROM backlinks WHERE target_url = 'example.com';
SELECT * FROM backlinks ORDER BY backlink_id DESC;
SELECT analysis_id, analysis_date, analysis_score FROM backlink_analysis WHERE analysis_score > 0.8;
SELECT target_url, anchor_text, source_domain FROM backlinks WHERE anchor_text LIKE '%SEO%';
SELECT * FROM backlinks WHERE backlink_status = TRUE ORDER BY anchor_text DESC
SELECT target_url, analysis_date FROM backlink_analysis WHERE analysis_score > 0.8 ORDER BY analysis_date ASC
SELECT source_domain, COUNT(*) AS total_backlinks FROM backlinks GROUP BY source_domain ORDER BY total_backlinks DESC
SELECT anchor_text, target_url, analysis_score FROM backlinks JOIN backlink_analysis ON backlinks.backlink_id = backlink_analysis.backlink_id WHERE analysis_score < 0.5 ORDER BY analysis_score ASC

SELECT source_domain, MAX(analysis_score) AS highest_score FROM backlinks JOIN backlink_analysis ON backlinks.backlink_id = backlink_analysis.backlink_id GROUP BY source_domain HAVING highest_score > 0.7
SELECT * FROM backlinks;
SELECT backlink_id, source_url, target_url FROM backlinks;
SELECT * FROM linked_pages WHERE page_title = 'Homepage';
SELECT page_url, page_title FROM linked_pages ORDER BY last_crawled DESC;
SELECT history_id, backlink_id, status, http_code FROM backlink_history WHERE status = 'active';
SELECT * FROM backlinks WHERE create_date > NOW() ORDER BY create_date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT source_url, target_url, anchor_text FROM backlinks WHERE source_url LIKE '%example%' ORDER BY create_date ASC;

SELECT b.backlink_id, h.status, h.http_code, h.check_date, b.source_url FROM backlinks b JOIN backlink_history h ON b.backlink_id = h.backlink_id WHERE h.http_code = 404 ORDER BY h.check_date DESC LIMIT 5;

SELECT p.page_url, p.page_title, COUNT(b.backlink_id) AS backlink_count FROM linked_pages p LEFT JOIN backlinks b ON p.page_id = b.backlink_id GROUP BY p.page_url, p.page_title HAVING backlink_count > 3 ORDER BY backlink_count DESC;

SELECT h.history_id, b.backlink_id, b.source_url, h.status, h.http_code, MAX(h.check_date) AS last_checked FROM backlinks b JOIN backlink_history h ON b.backlink_id = h.backlink_id GROUP BY h.history_id, b.backlink_id, b.source_url, h.status, h.http_code ORDER BY last_checked DESC;
SELECT * FROM Backlinks;
SELECT backlink_url, anchor_text, referring_domain FROM Backlinks;
SELECT target_url, target_rating FROM TargetPages ORDER BY target_rating DESC;
SELECT domain_name, domain_rating FROM ReferringDomains WHERE domain_rating > 50;
SELECT anchor_text_value, Backlinks.backlink_url FROM AnchorTexts JOIN Backlinks ON AnchorTexts.backlink_id = Backlinks.backlink_id;
SELECT * FROM Backlinks ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT backlink_url, referring_domain FROM Backlinks WHERE referring_domain='example.com';
SELECT anchor_text_value FROM AnchorTexts WHERE backlink_id=1;
SELECT target_url, target_rating FROM TargetPages WHERE target_rating > 50 ORDER BY target_rating DESC;
SELECT domain_name, domain_rating, created_at FROM ReferringDomains ORDER BY created_at;
SELECT * FROM backlinks;
SELECT url, anchor_text, domain_authority FROM backlinks ORDER BY domain_authority DESC;
SELECT name, domain FROM websites WHERE created_at >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY name ASC;
SELECT title, url FROM pages WHERE title LIKE '%keyword%' AND url IS NOT NULL;
SELECT author_id, name, email FROM authors ORDER BY created_at DESC, name ASC;
